Package: bugtractr
Type: Package
Title: Extract Data from Bugzilla Bug Tracker
Version: 0.9
Date: 2022-08-26
Authors@R: c(person("Mikko", "Korpela", role = c("aut", "cph", "cre"),
                    email = "mvkorpel@iki.fi"))
Author: Mikko Korpela [aut, cph, cre]
Maintainer: Mikko Korpela <mvkorpel@iki.fi>
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: base64enc, httr (>= 1.3.0), lubridate (>= 1.7.0), stringr (>= 0.4),
        tibble (>= 1.3.0), xml2
Description: List bugs by status, and get more information about selected bugs.
    The functions default to querying the R Bugzilla server but may also work
    for some other Bugzilla installations.
